---
layout: branded.hbs
subject: Customer Account Welcome
---
<table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
    {% if customer.name %}
    <tr>
        <td class="content-block"><h1>Dear \{{ customer.name }},</h1></td>
    </tr>
    {% endif %}
    <tr>
        <td class="content-block"><h2>An account has been created for you at \{{ shop.name }}.</h2></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td class="content-block">Please visit this url to activate your account and set your password.</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td class="content-block aligncenter"><a href="\{{ customer.account_activation_url }}" class="btn-primary">Active Your Account</a></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td class="content-block">If the account was created in error, you can visit the link above and select "Decline" to decline this invitation.</td>
    </tr>
</table>
